# In generated projects, .agent/ is local-only by default because the root
# .gitignore ignores .agent/.
#
# In the framework repository, this file must not hide the publishable scaffold
# under template/.agent/, so the core routing files are explicitly kept visible.
*
!.gitignore
!README.md
!ROSTER.md
!workflows/
!workflows/**
!skills/
!skills/README.md
